name: Shadowplay

deck: While hosting her first Trill initiate Dax discovers a tiny, expanding protouniverse that threatens to destroy the Bajoran system.

deck: When a Cardassian freighter explodes at Deep Space 9, the Cardassians blame Federation colonists in the new Demilitarized Zone.
description: This episode helps set up the next Star Trek series Star Trek Voyager.

deck: Three old Klingon warriors reunite on Deep Space 9, seeking Curzon Dax, with whom they entered into a blood oath to one day exact revenge on an enemy for killing the warriors' firstborn sons. Finding Jadzia as worthy a warrior as they felt Curzon to be, she joins the Klingons in completing their vendetta.
name: Blood Oath

deck: It's Halloween and Buffy, Willow, Xander and Oz are invited to a party in a haunted house.
name: Fear Itself

deck: Sisko tries to rescue Gul Dukat, stop the Maquis terrorists, and prevent a new war with the Cardassians.
name: The Maquis, Part II

deck: Bashir tries to help when Garak suffers painful headaches from an implant in his brain.
name: The Wire

deck: An accident inside the wormhole sends Kira and Bashir into the "mirror universe", where Klingons, Cardassians, and Bajorans rule over their human slaves.
description:
This was the first DS9 that featured the mirror universe visited in Mirror Mirror in the Original Series.

Avery Brooks, Nana Visitor, Rene Auberjonois, Colm Meany play their respective characters and their respective mirror universe characters.

Siddig El Fadil, Terry Farrell only played their respective characters.

Armin Shimerman and Andrew Robinson only played their respective mirror characters.
name: Crossover

deck: A Bajoran terrorist tests Kira's loyalties to the Federation when he attempts to rid Bajor of the Federation for good.
name: Past Prologue

deck: An old enemy of Odo's is murdered behind locked doors, and all the evidence points to Odo as the killer.
name: A Man Alone

deck: While investigating a massive explosion that destroyed all life on a planet, Janeway and Paris are swept back a day in time, where they must prevent the explosion.
name: Time and Again

deck: The Charmed ones must deal with a court case, that involves demons. Phoebe meets Cole.
name: The Honeymoon's Over

deck: While the sisters try to keep Piper and Leo wedding a secret, they must help a couple who has been cursed by demon.
name: Magic Hour

deck: The charmed ones help a girl called Kate,  protect a fairy princess Thistle from trolls. Cole Turner try to steal the Book of Shadows.

name: All Halliwell's Eve

deck: While the world's criminals continue to drop dead, L meets by computer with representatives from various nations.

name: Sight Unseen

deck: After a spell backfires, Prue is  given the unwanted gift of feeling all the pain in the world. Phoebe and Cole sleep together.

deck: With a second Kira now on the loose, L asks Light to join the task force and pose as the real Kira in order to catch the copycat.
